  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ControlFlowException, java.io.Serializable

    public class ServiceNotReadyException
extends ProcessCanceledException
    If thrown during startup process, indicates that a given service (e.g. index) isn't yet available, and the query should be re-attempted later.
